  m_text: "On your turn, click and \ndrag your ball to shoot!\n\nEvery stroke, any\nplayers
    that fall into the\nhole are eliminated.\n\nIf no one falls into the\nhole on
    a given stroke,\nthe person furthest\nfrom the hole will be\neliminated instead.\n\nLast
    ball standing wins\nthe hole and gains a point.\n\nFirst one to 3 points wins!"
